items.title: Mongo the Monkey
items.description: A cuddly stuffed animal monkey with soft brown fur and a playful expression.

items.title: Express the Pigeon
items.description: A plush stuffed animal pigeon featuring gray feathers and a gentle, watchful gaze.

items.title: React the Rhino
items.description: A large rhino, boasting a rugged gray hide and imposing horns, exuding a sturdy yet endearing presence.

items.title: Node the Chameleon
items.description: A plush, green chameleon and big, expressive eyes.

items.title: Python
items.description: A plush python with a colorful yellow and white pattern, perfect for reptile enthusiasts of all ages.

items.title: Elephant
items.description: Soft grey plush adorned with lifelike wrinkles and large, floppy ears that stand out. This plushie companion is both cuddly and ready to be a loyal playmate.

items.title: Bunnie
items.description: Its fluffy fur a soft shade of sunny yellow. With bright, expressive eyes and long, floppy ears.

items.title: Basset Hound
items.description: With floppy ears and soulful eyes, crafted from soft, velvety fabric in shades of brown and white. Its low-slung body and droopy expression capture the gentle charm of this beloved breed.

items.title: Whale
items.description: Crafted from soft, plush fabric in shades of deep ocean blue. The perfect cuddly companion for underwater adventures and cozy hugs.

items.title: Pufferfish
items.description: A charming pufferfish plushie, featuring soft, textured fabric in light hues of green and white. Capture the whimsy of the ocean, making it a delightful plush friend.

items.title: Octopus
items.description: This adorable purple octopus captures the playful spirit of the ocean, making it a perfect companion for imaginative underwater adventures and cuddly hugs.

items.title: Owl
items.description: A plush owling with soft, feathery fabric in shades of brown and white, adorned with bright, perceptive eyes.

items.title: Woodpecker
items.description: Capture the charm of this beloved woodland creature, making it an ideal plush companion for nature-inspired play and cozy snuggles.

items.title: Hummingbird
items.description: This enchanting plush captures the grace and beauty of these vibrant birds, making it a delightful companion for flights of fancy and tender moments of play.

items.title: Teddy Bear
items.description: This teddy bear stuffed animal, nearly four feet long, with plush fur so soft it begs for hugs. Its warm brown coat makes it the ultimate cuddle buddy for both children and adults alike.

items.title: Giraffe
items.description: Standing tall with its striking pattern of golden spots against a creamy coat of soft fur. Its kind eyes and gentle expression capture the essence of these graceful creatures.

items.title: Panda Bear
items.description: Adorable panda bear stuffed animal, crafted with velvety plush fur and irresistible charm, perfect for cuddles and companionship.

items.title: Koala Bear
items.description: With its fluffy fur and rounded ears, this adorable plush koala bear is perfect for cuddling and playtime.

items.title: Seal
items.description: Soft and cuddly seal plushie with a smooth coat of gray fur, perfect for both cuddles and imaginative ocean adventures.
